long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing the SummGen - summary extension for Google and YouTube: 
Powered by ChatGPT, this tool enhances your browsing experience by providing concise summaries alongside your Google search results and YouTube video descriptions. 

With a single glance, gain insights and overviews without having to click on every link or video. It's the perfect tool for quick research, video browsing, or simply staying informed. 

Elevate your search and streaming experience with summaries generated on the go!
